social_posts.post_text: With everything going on in the world right now i often feel helpless yet its hard not to feel the pain of everyone who is mourning and suffering in these uncertain times, for now my only outlet is music so i send this into the ether, in hopes that God will chanel it through the moon and stars to find those who need it most🙏🏾
Making hits from my hotel room lmao when inspiration hits you can’t ignore it 😎🤓🕺🏾 ps. if you love me and you love music then you’ll use headphones 😉🫶🏾

What a year this has been! All i can say is that i’m grateful for all the beautiful places i’ve seen all the beautiful people i’ve met and all the beautiful music i’ve made along the way, 10 clips is definitely not enough to capture the amount of moments that have made me grin from ear to ear. I’m so hype to see what 2024 is going to bring i know it’s gonna be a movie 😎 see y’all on the other side😊✌🏾🎶
Saw some really beautiful things today😍🤭
It’s been a minute since i’ve been able to just sit, connect with myself and play piano😮‍💨 feels like breathing air for the first time💆🏾‍♂️🪐
Dazzling the kiddos with a bunch of notes lol🤓 after people started gathering it low key ended up becoming an impromptu concert in the middle of this mall 😂 gotta keep that tip bucket on me lmao☠️
